wiki.summary: "In Ha Mood" is a song by Ice Spice. The song was initially teased via her social media accounts on the day of December 20, 2022 before being released to YouTube and SoundCloud on December 25, 2022 as the third single off of her debut EP "Like..?", the song was later uploaded to streaming platforms on January 6, 2023. The song is mostly about a woman who is taking control of her own destiny. Ice Spice celebrates her independence and success in life, expressing how she is in her own mood and light. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: "In Ha Mood" is a song by Ice Spice. The song was initially teased via her social media accounts on the day of December 20, 2022 before being released to YouTube and SoundCloud on December 25, 2022 as the third single off of her debut EP "Like..?", the song was later uploaded to streaming platforms on January 6, 2023. The song is mostly about a woman who is taking control of her own destiny. Ice Spice celebrates her independence and success in life, expressing how she is in her own mood and light. She has discovered her power, drives ambition and has achieved financial success. The message is to never stay stuck in the same place and to follow your dreams, even when it seems hard. It is also an encouragement to women to take control of their own lives and to be empowered. Read more on Last.fm.
